# Interview Guides - NEVER COMMIT THESE
# Guides contain discussion points, expected answers, and red flags
# that candidates should not see in advance

# Block the actual interview guides (generic and language-specific)
INTERVIEW_GUIDE.md
**/INTERVIEW_GUIDE.md
INTERVIEW_GUIDE_[A-Z]*.md
**/interview-guide*.md
.interview-guides/
interview-guides/

# Allow management documentation (these are safe, for interviewers)
!INTERVIEW_GUIDE_SHARED_DRIVE_README.md
!INTERVIEW_GUIDE_MIGRATION_NOTICE.md

# Language-specific interview artifacts (if generated in main by mistake)
INTERVIEW_PYTHON.md
INTERVIEW_NODEJS.md
INTERVIEW_CSHARP.md
INTERVIEW_GO.md
INTERVIEW_JAVA.md

